[$DQ$WFT_NPSS_P_1304_1710146843033_0$DQ$,$DQ$DS_1710333951252$DQ$,$DQ$M$DQ$,$DQ$S$DQ$,$DQ$ select  distinct NPSST_ID,  DATEMI,  ACCP_DATE_TIME,  CHANNEL_ID,  INTRBK_STTLM_CUR,  REVERSAL_AMOUNT, EXT_PURPOSE_CODE,  CLRSYSREF,  CREATED_DATE,  CHANNEL_ID,  ORIGINATOR_REF_NUMBER,  TRAN_AMOUNT,  PROCESS_NAME from  (  select   A.NPSST_ID,   A.VALUE_DATE,   to_char(A.VALUE_DATE, $SQ$DD/MM/YYYY$SQ$) as VALUEDATE,   A.CREATED_DATE,   A.CDTR_ACCT_NO,   A.CDTR_ACCT_NAME,   A.INTRBK_STTLM_AMNT,   A.INTRBK_STTLM_AMNT as TRAN_AMOUNT,   A.REVERSAL_AMOUNT,   A.INTRBK_STTLM_CUR, A.CR_SORT_CODE,   A.DEPARTMENT_CODE,   A.UETR,   A.EXT_PURPOSE_CODE,   A.PRODUCT_CODE,   A.CHANNEL_ID,   A.PROCESS_TYPE,   A.DBTR_IBAN,   A.CDTR_IBAN,   A.CLRSYSREF,   A.PAYMENT_ENDTOEND_ID as SENDER_REFERENCE_NUMBER,   A.ACCP_DATE_TIME,   A.EXHF_ID,   A.TENANT_ID,   A.PROCESSING_SYSTEM,   A.TRAN_REF_ID as ORIGINATOR_REF_NUMBER,   case    when A.EXHF_ID is null then UPPER($SQ$RCT$SQ$)    else UPPER($SQ$BCT$SQ$)   end as PAYMENT_TYPE,   A.PROCESS_GROUP,   NTPL.NPSSTPL_ID,   NTPL.PROCESS_NAME,   NTPL.PROCESS_REF_NO,   TO_CHAR(A.CREATED_DATE, $SQ$YYYY-MM-DD HH:MI:SS:MS AM$SQ$) as DATEMI, NPSS_TRANSACTIONS A  inner join NPSS_TRN_PROCESS_LOG NTPL on   A.UETR = NTPL.UETR  inner join CORE_SYSTEM_EXTN CSE on   CSE.department_code = A.DEPARTMENT_CODE  left join CORE_MEMBER_BANKS CMB on   CMB.BIC_CODE = A.CR_SORT_CODE   and CMB.NEED_SYNC = $SQ$Y$SQ$  where   NTPL.PROCESS_NAME in ($SQ$Place Pacs.007$SQ$)   and A.process_type = $SQ$OP$SQ$   or NTPL.PROCESS_NAME in($SQ$Receive Pacs.007$SQ$)   and A.process_type = $SQ$IP$SQ$)VW  $WHERE order by
